<h1 class="hero-h">Treetop AI: <em>which one are you looking for?</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">If you searched for "Treetop AI" you could have landed on any of several unrelated products that happen to share the name. This page sorts them out in ten seconds and points you to the right place. We are Treetop Growth Strategy, the AI-native go-to-market consultancy. We are not the voice platform, the finance app, or the travel product, but we will gladly send you to whichever one you actually want.</p>
</div></div>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">The short answer</span>
<h2 class="h2">Four different Treetops, one name</h2>
<p class="body answer">There is no single "Treetop AI." The name is used by at least four unrelated things: <strong>gettreetop.ai</strong>, an AI voice platform pitched as an AI sales engineer; a consumer <strong>Treetop personal-finance app</strong> for budgeting and money management; <strong>treetop.app</strong>, a travel product; and us, <strong>Treetop Growth Strategy</strong>, a consultancy that helps B2B teams build AI-native go-to-market motions. They share a word, not an owner. Pick the box below that matches what you came for.</p>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">Route me</span>
<h2 class="h2">Find the Treetop you meant</h2>
<div class="route-grid">

<div class="route-card">
<h3>The AI voice platform</h3>
<div class="who">gettreetop.ai</div>
<p>You want the AI voice tool: a voice agent pitched as an AI sales engineer that takes action and sounds like your smartest employee. That is gettreetop.ai, a separate company and product. Read our independent take, then go straight to the source.</p>
<a class="go" href="/gettreetop-ai-review">Read the gettreetop.ai review &rarr;</a>
</div>

<div class="route-card">
<h3>Help putting AI to work</h3>
<div class="who">Treetop Growth Strategy (us)</div>
<p>You want a partner to help your B2B team actually deploy AI across go-to-market: pick the right tools, wire them into a revenue motion, and ship workflows that produce results. That is what we do. Start with the free Gap Assessment.</p>
<a class="go" href="/quiz" >Take the Gap Assessment &rarr;</a>
</div>

<div class="route-card">
<h3>The personal-finance app</h3>
<div class="who">Treetop finance app (separate)</div>
<p>You want the consumer Treetop app for budgeting and personal money management. That is an unrelated product we do not build or support. Search for the Treetop finance app directly in your app store; you are in the wrong place here.</p>
<a class="go" href="/">Back to Treetop Growth Strategy &rarr;</a>
</div>

<div class="route-card">
<h3>The travel product</h3>
<div class="who">treetop.app (separate)</div>
<p>You want treetop.app, a travel product. Also unrelated to us. Head to treetop.app directly. If you ended up here looking for travel, this is not it, but now you know where to go.</p>
<a class="go" href="/">Back to Treetop Growth Strategy &rarr;</a>
</div>

</div>
<div class="disclosure">Disclosure: gettreetop.ai is a separate company and product. We have no affiliate or referral arrangement with it and are not paid to mention it. We point to it because clients ask us about voice tools and it is a clear example of the category. The Treetop finance app and treetop.app are likewise unrelated to us. Confirm any product's details on its own site. See our <a href="/gettreetop-ai-review">gettreetop.ai review</a> for our independent view.</div>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">If you meant us</span>
<h2 class="h2">What Treetop Growth Strategy actually does</h2>
<p class="body">If you were looking for help making AI work in your business, you are in the right place. Treetop Growth Strategy is an AI-native go-to-market consultancy for B2B teams. We help companies roll out Claude and AI tooling, hire fractional revenue leadership, and rebuild their go-to-market motion for the AI era. Voice agents are one piece of that picture, not the whole thing.</p>
<p class="body">The way we frame voice tools matters: a voice agent is a channel inside a motion, not a strategy. A platform like gettreetop.ai, Vapi, Retell, or Synthflow only pays off when the rest of your motion catches what it produces, when the booking lands in your CRM, a human picks up the hot calls, and the follow-up fires. Designing that wiring, and deciding whether voice belongs in your stack at all, is exactly the work our <a href="/services/ai-audit">AI Audit</a> exists for. For the bigger picture, see <a href="/the-ai-native-gtm-framework">the AI-native GTM framework</a> and <a href="/best-ai-voice-platforms-2026">best AI voice platforms 2026</a>.</p>
</div></section>

<section><div class="sec-inner">
<span class="lbl">FAQ</span>
<h2 class="h2">Common questions</h2>
<div class="faq-q">What is Treetop AI?</div>
<p class="body">Treetop AI is not one thing. Several unrelated products use the name: gettreetop.ai (an AI voice platform), a consumer Treetop personal-finance app, treetop.app (a travel product), and Treetop Growth Strategy (an AI-native go-to-market consultancy). They share a word, not an owner. Figure out which job you need done, and the right one becomes obvious.</p>
<div class="faq-q">Is gettreetop.ai related to Treetop Growth Strategy?</div>
<p class="body">They are separate. gettreetop.ai is a software product, an AI voice platform. Treetop Growth Strategy is a consultancy that helps B2B teams build AI-native go-to-market motions. We cover voice tools, including gettreetop.ai, because our clients ask about them, but we do not own that product and have no affiliate arrangement with it.</p>
<div class="faq-q">Which Treetop AI is the voice platform?</div>
<p class="body">The AI voice platform is gettreetop.ai, pitched as the AI voice platform that takes action and sounds like your smartest employee. If you want the voice tool, go to its site directly. If you want help deciding whether and how a voice agent fits your business, that is the kind of work Treetop Growth Strategy does.</p>
<div class="faq-q">Which Treetop AI is the finance app?</div>
<p class="body">The consumer personal-finance product is a separate Treetop app focused on budgeting and money management for individuals. It is unrelated to the AI voice platform and to our consultancy. If you are looking for a personal finance tool, search for the Treetop finance app directly; it is not something we build or support.</p>
</div></section>

